1�The sealed ruins in the Woh Gates must lead to the Serpentine Labyrinth. I can feel it.
1�Umbrils fighting leafkin!? What on Vana'diel is going on?
1�M-Morimar? But that's the name of the founder king's general--
1�You know about the sword? But...I mean... Just look at you!
1�I'm not quite sure I understand. Who exactly needs convincing?
1�(Quite the confused melee we have stumbled into.)
1�(Hmph. Like you would ever lose before I got here.)
1�(Fate binds us together, Morimar. You know that.)
1�(And surely we have better things to do than sit here casting aspersions at one another.)
t!�<Huff>...Numberless horde, indeed! I hack 'n hack but they keep on comin'!
1�Got 'em all cleaned up? Hafta admit, ya've got more spunk than I'da thought possible!
1�Yo, Darrcuiln! Those eyes of yers're sharper than I gave 'em credit for! Bwahaha!
1�Well, I'll be--Arciela! Ya've grown, that's fer sure!
1�It's been ages since someone's called me that, and I'da thought to never hear it again...but yes, I'm that Morimar.
1�Glad ta see that Ortharsyne's been kept safe all these years.
1�It's been much more'n a few moons since I've seen it, and I am gettin' on in years...
1�But ya dinn't come here to listen to me ramble.Yer in search of the scales, right?
1�Haha, it takes a wolf to know the heart of a beast!Not that I think yer a beast...
1�Grrr....that's rich comin' from ya! Sometimes I wonder why I don' just throw ya into the Zoldeff River.
1�<Sigh>I've been at this for a long time, and I've ne'er had as smart-aleck of a companion as this lump of fur.
1�Got that right! Back to the matter at hand...I've got an idea where ya can find those scales yer lookin' for.
1�'Course, nothin's sure in the muddied waters of Ulbuka, but even the smallest possibility's better'n nothin'.But if you want to find 'em, you'll need to convince him.
1�Ah, the spirit of youth! Good to see yer so eager to keep on top of things.
1�This whole ??colonization?? thing is best left to the young. Ol' fuddy-duddies like me have no place in...Ho-ho, better stop m'self before I get further off track.
1�I'm talkin' 'bout Sajj'aka of course. If you want to find the scales, you're gonna need to convince him. And I'll come along to help.
1�We're runnin' outta time, we need to hurry. I made a promise to August and I don't intend to break it!

1�Oh my Gob! You're one of those adventurerurers, aren't ya?You got nothin' on me, ?[man./lady.] I was just mindin' my own businesesess, lookin' for junk an' stuff.
1�Hey, watch out. You don't wanna fight me. I'll turn you into meat jerky!Wait, how about you and me be friends instead? Sound good?
